This package contains code for abstract intepretation (type inference)
and run-time code-generation of Lau code.  Both of these featuers use
a lower-lever representation of byte-codes (aka Micro Lua).
Modules of interest:

  * Galua.Micro.AST: asbtract syntax for micro Lua
  * Galua.Micro.JIT: compilation of Micro Lua (via Haskell and GHC)
  * Galua.Micro.Translate(.*): translation from Lua byte-code to Micro Lua
  * Galua.Micro.Type.*: abstract interpretation of Micro Lua


